cabins.name: Randaberg Resort
cabins.description: Resort is situated in Bodø and features air-conditioned accommodation with free WiFi, as well as access to a terrace.

cabins.name: Maybua Hytta
cabins.description: Maybua is located in the picturesque fishing village Bodø. This traditional waterfront house offers free WiFi.

cabins.name: Holmen Plaza
cabins.description: Situated 3.5 km from the picturesque Tverlandet fishing village, these waterfront fishermen’s cottages include a kitchenette, seating area and balcony with sea views.

cabins.name: Lærvig Hytta
cabins.description: Boasting a garden, barbecue facilities, and a terrace, Sea-view house in Bodø offers accommodation in Bodø with free WiFi and lake views.

cabins.name: Gravdal Hus
cabins.description: This property offers traditional fishing cottages with sea views. Guests can try a wood-fired hot tub or activities such as fishing, kayaking and hiking. WiFi is in some cottages.

cabins.name: Bøstad Resort
cabins.description: Guests are welcome to enjoy the free WiFi. The holiday home offers a terrace. Guests can also relax in the garden.

cabins.name: Kabelvåg Huset
cabins.description: Situated in the well-known beach of Kjøpsvik, seaside villa features an outdoor swimming pool and solarium. Guests benefit from Kjøpsvik sea views.

cabins.name: Sanden Plass
cabins.description: Located 100 metres from the centre of the Ballangen Town and 80 metres from the beach, Sanden offers air-conditioned apartments with furnished balcony overlooking the Nordic Sea.

cabins.name: Raften Studios
cabins.description: Featuring an outdoor pool with a covered terrace, Raften Studios are located in Ballangen. It is within a 5-minute walk from the beach and the centre of the Fishing Town.

cabins.name: Kongsvika
cabins.description: Boasting sea views, Kongsvika features accommodation with a balcony and a kettle, around 3 km from Stjørdal. It has city views and free WiFi throughout the property.

cabins.name: Ulvik Resort
cabins.description: Ulvik Resort is 1 km from Stjørdal, the island's main area, and offers air-conditioned accommodation. Free WiFi access is available. The nearest kebab place is 1.5 km away.

cabins.name: Villa Dyrøya
cabins.description: Located just 50 metres from the beach, Villa Dyrøya offers rooms and apartments that open to balconies with sea view. It features a garden and a sun terrace.

cabins.name: Stein Rossvolstad
cabins.description: Stein Rossvolstad is situated in Snillfjord. This villa provides air-conditioned accommodation with free WiFi. The villa is equipped with a flat-screen TV and 2 bedrooms

cabins.name: Grønnbus Hytta Plaza
cabins.description: Grønnbus Hytta Plaza is located 2 km from Melandsjø and offers ground-level accommodation in Melandsjø. Plaza features views to Nordic and the sea. Free WiFi is provided.

cabins.name: Skalandslys Apartments
cabins.description: Offering free WiFi and garden views, Skalandslys Apartments is an accommodation located in Øvre Ervik, just 450 metres from closest town and 700 metres from Cornflakes Garden.

cabins.name: Mjelde Studios
cabins.description: Featuring sea views, Mjelde Studios offers accommodation with barbecue facilities, around 1.7 km from Bergen downtown. This property offers access to a balcony, free private parking and free WiFi.
